</paragraph>
<paragraph id="3329D4243B3A2CC52CAD3BB33C7F855D" pageId="14" pageNumber="131">
Holotype, ♂: BRAZIL - SC [Santa Catarina], 
<normalizedToken id="C8DF787E873D5585721902E725D5450C" originalValue="São">Sao</normalizedToken>
Bento do Sul, Rio Natal, 550 m. XI.2013. A. Rank leg/ 27.473 Col. C. Mielke / C. Mielke diss.: 27.473/ DZ 32.729/ HOLOTYPE male 
<taxonomicName id="AC8A344BCAF21299144EB6F8AC810697" authority="St Laurent &amp; C.Mielke, 2016" authorityName="St Laurent &amp; C.Mielke" authorityYear="2016" class="Insecta" family="Mimallonidae" genus="Auroriana" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Auroriana gemma" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="14" pageNumber="131" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="gemma">Auroriana gemma</taxonomicName>
St Laurent and C. Mielke, 2016 [handwritten red label]/ (DZUP). Type locality: Brazil: Santa Catarina: 
<normalizedToken id="A644E67F25462218193233ECA79A18CB" originalValue="São">Sao</normalizedToken>
Bento do Sul, Rio Natal.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="F5F934FEEFAD5FCFDB38993FACA8C5A6" pageId="14" pageNumber="131">
Paratype, 1 ♂: BRAZIL: Santa Catarina: Neu Bremen [
