]: III.1938, B. Pohl (MZSP). Paratype with the following yellow label: PARATYPE male 
<taxonomicName id="1886716B1F9944DCE6E9D2F95CEDFC75" authority="St Laurent &amp; C.Mielke, 2016" authorityName="St Laurent &amp; C.Mielke" authorityYear="2016" class="Insecta" family="Mimallonidae" genus="Auroriana" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Auroriana gemma" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="14" pageNumber="131" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="gemma">Auroriana gemma</taxonomicName>
